note.body:
This is crashing in a function that was added in 3.4.8, which explains
why you don't see it with 3.4.7.  I don't think the glib issue is
related.

I can't reproduce this myself.  Are you using any non-default plugins?
Are you running rhythmbox in GNOME or some other type of desktop
session?

Can you try running rhythmbox under gdb and setting a breakpoint on
rb-ext-db.c:impl_finalize and see if it gets hit before the crash?
